releaseNotes:
OrderService:
      Added support for application specific data on Order, DeliveryNote and Invoice.

      - New Collection, InfoList, used to keep application specific data on Order, DeliveryNote and Invoice.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Collections

      - New Property, Info, on Order, DeliveryNote and Invoice. See InfoList above.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/DeliveryNote
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/Invoice
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/Order

      - New Entity, Info.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Orders/Entities/Info

      ProductService:
      Minor additions on Product and ProductItem

      - New Property, IsSubscribable, on Product and ProductItem. Used for Subscriptions, see ShoppingService below.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Products/Entities/Product
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Products/Entities/ProductItem

      ShoppingService:
      Now supporting creation of recurring orders with the use of Subscriptions. Not 100% completed yet.
      One minor addition to Promotion.

      - New Collections, SheduleList, SubscriptionList and SubscriptionTypeList. Used for Subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Collections

      - New Property, IsSubscribable on BasketItem. Can be used to see if a BasketItem can be copied to a Subscription. Not fully implemented.

      - New Entity, Subscription. Defines a Subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Entities/Subscription

      - New Entity, SubscriptionSchedule. Defines a schedule for a Subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Entities/SubscriptionSchedule

      - New Entity, SubscriptionSheduleData. General data for scheduling Subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Entities/SubscriptionScheduleData

      - New Entity, SubscriptionType. A SubscriptionType specified for the application. Used by Subscription. SubscriptionTypes are created in StormAdmin.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Entities/SubscriptionType

      - New Method, CreateSubscription. Used to create subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/CreateSubscription

      - New Method, GetSubscription. Used to get a subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/GetSubscription

      - New Method, GetSubscriptionScheduleData. Used to get meta data for scheduling subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/GetSubscriptionScheduleData

      - New Method, ListSubscriptions. Used to list active and old Subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/ListSubscriptions

      - New Method, ListSubscriptionStatus. Used to list available status ids for Subscriptions.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/ListSubscriptionStatus

      - New Method, ListSubscriptionTypes. Used to list all available SubscriptionTypes.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/ListSubscriptionTypes

      - New Method, PurchaseSubscription. Used to buy a Subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/PurchaseSubscription

      - New Method, UpdateSubscription. Used to update data on a Subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/UpdateSubscription

      - New Method, DeleteSubscription. Used to delete an active subscription.
      https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/#/Shopping/Operations/DeleteSubscription
title: Enferno Storm Api Client
